<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Admin Guide - JavaCoder Platform</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    .section-title {
      border-left: 5px solid #dc3545;
      padding-left: 15px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .guide-card {
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }
    .guide-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/dashboard/admin">JavaCoder Admin</a>
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse">
        <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
          <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/dashboard/admin">Dashboard</a></li>
          <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/admin/settings">Settings</a></li>
          <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/auth/logout">Logout</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Guide Content -->
  <div class="container py-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4 text-danger fw-bold text-center">üìò Admin Panel Guide</h1>
    <p class="text-muted text-center">Everything you need to know to manage the JavaCoder Platform efficiently.</p>

    <div class="section-title mt-5">
      <h3>User Management</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="card guide-card mb-4">
      <div class="card-body">
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Add or Remove Users:</strong> Use the "Manage Users" tab to create new users or delete existing ones.</li>
          <li><strong>Assign Roles:</strong> Choose from Student, Teacher, or Admin while creating users.</li>
          <li><strong>Reset Passwords:</strong> Admins can manually reset user credentials if needed.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">
      <h3>Teacher Transfer System</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="card guide-card mb-4">
      <div class="card-body">
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Monitor Ratings:</strong> Teachers with a rating above 4.0 can be promoted or transferred.</li>
          <li><strong>Approve Transfers:</strong> Navigate to the ‚ÄúTeacher Requests‚Äù section to review and approve transfer requests.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">
      <h3>Course Oversight</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="card guide-card mb-4">
      <div class="card-body">
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Course Creation:</strong> Ensure courses follow curriculum guidelines before approving them.</li>
          <li><strong>Teacher Assignments:</strong> Assign certified teachers to relevant courses.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">
      <h3>Platform Monitoring</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="card guide-card mb-4">
      <div class="card-body">
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Activity Logs:</strong> Keep track of user activity for security and analysis.</li>
          <li><strong>Security:</strong> Ensure only verified users access sensitive routes.</li>
          <li><strong>Performance:</strong> Check loading times and error reports regularly.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-5">
      <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-danger">Back to Admin Dashboard</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
